lead_paragraph: Coming around second base in the seventh inning of the Pittsburgh Pirates' 8-4 victory over the Chicago Cubs on Wednesday night, John Jaso stumbled.

headline.print_headline: Jaso Hits for Cycle as Pirates Beat Cubs 8-4
